text: haey chaur puok anak kom thveu dauch srei d mneak del ban thveu aoy ambaoh hong robsa neang khauch kraoypi neang ban mour vea nen haey noh aoy saoh . puok anak yk kar sbath robsa puok anak mk baokabanhchhot rveang puok anak khluoneng prohte yl tha krom muoy brasaer cheang krom muoytiet . pitabrakd nasa a l laoh kreante sakalbong puok anak bonnaoh . haey trong pitchea nung banhcheak yeang chbasa dl puok anak now thngai barlok nouv avei del puok anak thleab ban khvengkoumnit knea noh
